pageContext.claim: “'There is no possible way the Trump Tower meeting between Don Trump jr and a couple of Russians, who have very deep connections to both the Clintons & Fusion GPS, & where no information on the Clintons was exchanged, is a crime. Dems are blinded by their hatred of Trump.' Bongino”
pageContext.analysis: The Fox News commentator Trump is quoting in this tweet is not a lawyer. Special counsel Robert Mueller's team continues to investigate Russia's interference in the 2016 election and has not announced whether or not Russia cooperated with Trump's campaign. There's no evidence that the Kremlin-connected lawyer who met with Trump Jr. during the campaign, Natalia Veselnitskaya, has any ties to the Clintons.
